Template: emoncms/address
Type: string
Default: http://localhost/
Description: Emoncms address:
 Enter the URL of emoncms web server

Template: emoncms/authentication
Type: string
Default: 
Description: Emoncms API Key:
 Enter the API Key of the emoncms user

Template: openmuc/mysql_host
Type: string
Default: 3306
Description: MySQL host name:
 Enter the host name of the MySQL database

Template: openmuc/mysql_port
Type: string
Default: 3306
Description: MySQL port:
 Enter the port of the MySQL database

Template: openmuc/mysql_database
Type: string
Default: emondata
Description: MySQL database name:
 Enter the name of the MySQL database

Template: openmuc/mysql_user
Type: string
Default: emoncms
Description: MySQL user name:
 Enter the name for the user of the MySQL database

Template: openmuc/mysql_password
Type: password
Default: 
Description: MySQL user password:
 Enter the password for the user of the MySQL database
